Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At least tell us what you\Nthink of the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that this incident\Nis one of the serial murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The victims, the Joppes,\Ndid they have any children?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,this is exactly like the murders\Nof middle-aged couples
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that have been happening\Nthroughout Germany!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that an agent from the BKA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,who's in charge of that case\Nhas come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that there's\Na connection to the serial killings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it would be quicker\Nto ask the BKA agent directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get ahead of the other papers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me a giant space\Nfor the headline.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kipper from the Hamburg Tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the agent from the BKA,\Naren't you? I'd like a comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a connection between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,this case and the other murders\Nof middle-aged couples?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kipper of the Hamburg Tag...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you an exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's precisely correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This case is one of the murders\Nof middle-aged couples!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so! Then the suspect is\Nthat Japanese doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw the report. It was carried out\Nin the same way as the other killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hamburg Tag is the leading\Npaper around here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect your article to be in\Nthe leading papers across Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Thank you\Nfor your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the culprit.\NI have just become the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I knock?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it would be best not to\Nstartle the Joppes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a friendly couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They casually welcome me in\Nand lead me to the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't suspicious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband's chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I sit in the guest chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband dies over there\Non the floor a few minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still haven't made my move.\NWhere is the wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, she still isn't in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be pouring out tea\Nin the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The wife is stabbed in the back\Nbefore she can serve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that I should\Nmake my move about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I take out my knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As the husband panics\Nand tries to stand up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I stab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband runs away\Nwith a wound on his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The next strike is on\Nthe husband's right shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss again. I'm really an amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband screams\Nhis wife's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But his wife, who's in the kitchen,\Ncannot hear him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife has become\Nhard of hearing lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I knew about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Make noise. Cry and scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take my time and deal with\Nyour wife after I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cornered you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband's left hand print.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cornered the husband\Nin front of this sideboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't finish him off here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 5 meters from where\Nthe husband died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I finish him off here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this man kill the Joppes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that may not be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to ask a favor\Nof everyone in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Behave normally if this man appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And give me a call\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be in any danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This was such a terrible incident\Nfor such a quiet neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. The Joppes were\Nreally good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Joppe always greeted me\Ncheerfully every morning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,when I called out to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When you called out to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Joppe became hard of hearing\Nabout a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was written on\Nher physician's medical chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She shouldn't have heard\Nmost of your greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:06:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing her, she probably greeted\Nme when she sensed my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't anyone in the neighborhood\Nknow about her hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... What a wonderful business\Nyou have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made such rapid progress\Nat such a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an easy thing to do, Mr.\NGiebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the contracts I made
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with car manufacturers\Njust happened to work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to give my sincere condolences\Nfor your uncle and aunt's misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My uncle and aunt\Nwere my only relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That couple never had any children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have taken good care\Nof you as their nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was if I was really their son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, will the culprit be caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm pretty sure I know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that Japanese ex-doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. There have been cases\Nlike this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How much will your inheritance be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Joppe was\Nquite a wealthy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that have something to do\Nwith this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the only heir to their estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it? That's not something\Nto be talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Companies can be hard on money\Neven if they seem to be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens often.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk as if I was\Nafter their inheritance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. You have a perfect alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You went out to dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with your secretary and subordinates\Nafter a business meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There are witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been investigating that nephew\Nfor the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,His company might look profitable\Nat first glance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's holding a lot of\Nbad stocks and bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty strapped for cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've even thoroughly investigated\Nthe area around the nephew's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think this case\Nis connected with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the middle-aged couple murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All the newspapers are taking\Nthe same take as our exclusive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a huge false report if it's\Nnot related to that string of murders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the work of a copycat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was made to look like\Nthe serial killer's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to rewrite\Nmy article immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's fine as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue writing your article\Nas if it was one of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the middle-aged couple murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't write an article of lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm still a journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless to pressure me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kipper, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She was quite an attractive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a comfortable household...\Na lovely wife and daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to resist the charms\Nof such an ideal, attractive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep writing features on the middle-\Naged couple murders as you've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, write even more about it\Nthan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He will come if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I wanted to\Nask you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. They were such\Na wonderful couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they have any foster children?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they ever live with any children\Nyou've never seen before,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,even for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Never. They took good care\Nof their nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Would you like another\Ncup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...no, I'm already...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistake.\NIt's the man from the photograph.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's in my house right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you\Nfor your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge, there's someone\Nwho wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the nephew of the Joppes\Nwho were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that I'm the culprit,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you? Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed them for their fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're really thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,True, I have countless debts\Nat the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Their fortune they left for me\Nwould save me from this fiasco.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not that kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you came here to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right to say that\Nafter treating me like the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have somewhere\NI have to go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I want you to take back\Nthe rude things you said before!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The police stopped following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The police here think you're innocent.\NIsn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who do you think\Nis the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I catch that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bloodstain there.\NWhich means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you don't think that\Nthe Japanese doctor did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a crime made to look like the string\Nof middle-aged couple homicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing in this case\Nthat the others don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit cornered the victim here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's finished off over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he hesitate for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There were emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime scenes\Nof the man I'm after...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes a few valuables and tries to\Nmake it look like a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But no emotions can be sensed\Nat those crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But this crime scene is full of\Nemotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit panics at the sight of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the victim's face\Nand his face in a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The police here are incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how I think about it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a crime made to look like\NJohan's crimes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How long is this going to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How long...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally meet, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to have\Na quiet talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use in\Nrunning away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a quiet talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to\Nkeep doing this, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you weren't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I did it. I killed the Joppes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn myself in! Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this wound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you're going to\Nbleed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who stabbed inspector Lunge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to drop him off\Nin front of a hospital and run away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the keys\Nto these handcuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless to look for your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just quickly hand me\Nthe keys to these handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, it hadn't penetrated\Nyour abdominal cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But the large amount of blood\Nyou're losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die if we don't\Nstop the bleeding!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess...Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You murdered the director\Nof Eisler Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,along with three others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been killing middle-aged\Ncouples for the past three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess that it was all your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all Johan's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking for the real culprit,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Johan, Dr. Tenma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything good\Nin this warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but I found what I needed\Nto perform an emergency procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left are these hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can save you as long as\Nthese hands are freed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a skillful doctor\Nwhen you're Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A good-natured man with no faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people did you kill\Nwith those hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to\Nchange into Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When is that good-natured face\Ngoing to turn into that of a killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're losing consciousness\Nas your blood pressure falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At your crime scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't talk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At your crime scenes...\Nthere are no emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You lose your emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,when you deal with life and death\Nevery day, don't you, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. That calmness\Nis always at the crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfectly calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I performed a surgery...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Would I make a mistake?\NCould I do this well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Would trouble happen\Nall of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always tense...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People's lives are at stake\Nwith my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that I can be calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stop your bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the keys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they in your pants pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You look better than\Nwhen you're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that that emergency\Nprocedure was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said that\Nyou would have died
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if it that exact procedure\Nwasn't performed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this means that Tenma\Nsaved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Tenma got away,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but Giebel confessed to\Nthe murder of the Joppes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You did good, Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma saved Lunge's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be problematic\Nin catching Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I remove Lunge\Nfrom the Tenma case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry if Inspector Lunge\Nis being a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:21:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a nuisance at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a very pleasant man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling him that he doesn't\Nhave to recover that quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's squeezing that ball\Nand walking down the halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like he's having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He keeps saying that\Nnothing could be more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that culprit's name?\NOh yes, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's said that he was having\Na wonderful time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,chasing a culprit like Tenma.
